text.tspan: [W]e have also equipped you with a
CAMS (Camera and monitoring
system) designed for you to see
what's going on. This should
eliminate the fear of anything being
with you
(Disclaimer! there is not a gurantee
that there isn't anything with you)
There also happens to be a large
vent conveniently placed behind you.
this vent is for the large industrial
[f]ans to keep this building cool. Some
Debris may come out of this vent, so
you have been provided a block to
keep that debris from bothering you.
Don't worry, this door does not draw
any power so there is no reason to
worry about that. Do not leave it
closed for too long though, as it may
build up pressure and fly right into
your back, which would be a pain for
our legal team.
(Building Power, Section III)
Press > arrow to
